sentences: Chinatsu Wakatsuki (若槻 千夏, Wakatsuki Chinatsu, born 28 May 1984) is a Japanese variety tarento and former gravure idol.
Her real name was Chiharu Kurihara (栗原 千春, Kurihara Chiharu) before she got married.
She is represented with Platinum Production.
Credited under the name Chinachable with the comedy duo Untouchable.
WC – Chinatsu Wakatsuki's Designed-Produced fashion brand (in Japanese)
